    "description": "Blue Dart Global Group, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Distribution Manager for our Amritsar operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Blue Dart Global Group:\nBlue Dart Global Group is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Amritsar, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Blue Dart Global Group!",
